    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    dc:creator "Paulsen, M. J." ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "Generic changes in the stag beetle tribe Aesalini (Coleoptera: Lucanidae: Aesalinae) with the description of two new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3710076>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3710078> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3710076>
    dc:description "Figures 1–2. Zelenka holotypes. 1) Holotype of Echinoaesalus jaechi Zelenka. a) Dorsal habitus. b) Abdomen, ventral view. c) Labels. 2) Holotype female of Echinoaesalus sabahensis Zelenka. a) Dorsal habitus. b) Abdomen, ventral view, showing complete leg-shaped sulci. c) Labels. Photos courtesy H. Schillhammer (Naturhistorisches Museum, Vienna)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3710076/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3710078>
    dc:description "Figures 3–5. Generic differences of ocular canthus/eye and clypeal apex. 3) Echinoaesalus spp. 4) Strabaesalus spp. 5) Zelenkaesalus spp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3710078/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

